 Available experimental data were interpreted  using              3928 1451
 nuclear reaction model code EMPIRE-2.19b31 by                    3928 1451
 M. Herman et al [He01, He02]. This code integrates               3928 1451
 into a single system a number of important modules               3928 1451
 and features:                                                    3928 1451
                                                                  3928 1451
 - Spherical and deformed Optical Model including                 3928 1451
   coupled-channels (ECIS03 by J. Raynal)                         3928 1451
 - Hauser-Feshbach statistical model including                    3928 1451
   HRTW width fluctuation correction                              3928 1451
 - Quantum-mechanical MSD TUL model (codes ORION &                3928 1451
   TRISTAN by H. Lenske), and MSC NVWY model                      3928 1451
 - Exciton model with angular momentum coupling                   3928 1451
   (code DEGAS by E. Betak and P. Oblozinsky) that                3928 1451
   represents a good approximation to the DSD model               3928 1451
 - Exciton model with Iwamoto-Harada cluster                      3928 1451
   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 3928 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                3928 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   3928 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                3928 1451
   discrete transitions                                           3928 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL-2 library [Ri03]              3928 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                3928 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               3928 1451
   and gamma strength functions  based on the RIPL-2              3928 1451
   library [Ri03]                                                 3928 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              3928 1451
   EXFOR/CSISRS library                                           3928 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A. Trkov)                    3928 1451
   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 3928 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                3928 1451
   PrePro codes by R. Cullen                                      3928 1451
